# 🧠 DocuMorph AI — The All-In-One Smart Editing Suite

**Edit smarter, not harder.**
DocuMorph AI is a cross-platform web + mobile app that empowers users to **intuitively edit PDFs, Word docs, Excel sheets, screenshots, and scanned images** — even handwritten content — using **cutting-edge AI** for intelligent detection, rewriting, and layout preservation.

> Whether you're a student, professional, or designer — DocuMorph transforms how you edit and interact with documents.

---

## 🚀 Key Features

### 📤 Upload & Import

* Drag-and-drop PDFs, DOCX, XLSX, PNG, JPEG, or scanned files
* Capture documents via mobile camera

### 🔍 AI Recognition & Extraction

* OCR for printed + handwritten text
* Detects layout, tables, objects, logos, stamps
* Identifies watermarks and unwanted elements for removal

### ✍️ Smart Editing Tools

* In-place text editing with font/style matching
* AI grammar correction, rephrasing & multilingual support
* Font overlay for handwritten or printed text

### 🖼️ Object Removal & Background Inpainting

* Remove watermarks, logos, stamps
* Reconstruct clean backgrounds with generative AI
* Retain original formatting and layout

### ♻️ Format Conversion

* PDF ↔ DOCX ↔ TXT ↔ Image
* XLSX → PDF, Image → Editable Text

### 🧠 AI-Powered Enhancements

* Semantic search & AI summarizer
* Keyword extraction
* Text-to-speech narration (accessibility mode)
* Translation & rewriting across languages

### 📐 Layout Preservation

* Retain spacing, margins, and structure
* Auto-align and reflow content for clean visuals

### 📱 Cross-Platform Editing

* Web & mobile support (React + React Native/Flutter)
* Cloud sync and real-time collaboration (Coming Soon)

---

## 👥 Use Cases

| User Type           | What You Can Do                                                                |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| 🧑‍🎓 Students      | Fix handwritten assignments, summarize scanned notes, convert to editable text |
| 👩‍💼 Professionals | Edit contracts/reports, redact sensitive data, rephrase content                |
| 📸 Designers        | Modify mockups, update captions/logos, remove visual clutter                   |
| 🧑‍⚕️ Healthcare    | Digitize patient forms, improve readability of handwritten prescriptions       |
| 🧑‍🦽 Accessibility | Narrate documents, simplify layout, voice-based editing                        |

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

| Layer            | Tools & Frameworks                                                          |
| ---------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 💻 Frontend      | React, Tailwind CSS, React Native / Flutter                                 |
| ⚙️ Backend       | Node.js, Express, Firebase / MongoDB                                        |
| 🧠 AI & CV       | OpenCV, Tesseract OCR, EasyOCR, Segment Anything, Hugging Face Transformers |
| 📄 Doc Tools     | PDF.js, Mammoth.js (DOCX), SheetJS (Excel), LibreOffice SDK                 |
| ☁️ Cloud APIs    | Google Vision API, AWS Textract, Azure Form Recognizer                      |
| 🔊 Accessibility | Web Speech API, pyTTSx3                                                     |
| 🎨 Font Matching | FontTools, PIL, LayoutLM                                                    |

---

## 🛣️ Project Roadmap

| Phase             | Highlights                                                             |
| ----------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| ✅ MVP Launch      | Screenshot & PDF editing, OCR, layout detection, font overlay          |
| 🔄 Core Expansion | DOCX, Excel support, semantic search, rephrasing, multilingual editing |
| 📱 Mobile Beta    | On-device image-to-doc conversion, cloud sync                          |
| 🌟 Advanced Tools | Batch edits, export customization, browser extension, offline mode     |

